AI Elder Finance Protector

FULL PROJECT SETUP 
This includes:
1.	Backend setup (Flask + Scam Analyzer + Twilio SMS)
2.	Twilio API setup
3.	Frontend setup (your custom dashboard UI)
4.	Elder-UI Alerts
5.	Running both servers
6.	Testing alerts

STEP 1 — Create Project Folders
Create this structure:
ai-elder-protector/
│
├── backend/
└── frontend/

STEP 2 — Install Python & Create Backend
2.1 Open CMD inside backend folder:
cd backend
2.2 Create virtual environment:
python -m venv venv
2.3 Activate virtual environment:
venv\Scripts\activate
2.4 Install backend libraries:
pip install flask flask-cors requests twilio
2.5 Create app.py inside backend

STEP 3 — Create Twilio SMS API
You must set up Twilio one time only.
3.1 Go to Twilio
https://www.twilio.com
3.2 Create free account
They give:
•	1 free trial phone number
•	Free trial credits
•	Ability to send SMS to verified numbers
3.3 Get your credentials
Go to Console → Dashboard
You will get:
•	ACCOUNT SID → looks like: ACxxxxxxxxxxxxx
•	AUTH TOKEN → looks like: aPxxxxxxxxxxxxx
•	TWILIO PHONE NUMBER → looks like: +19804042373
3.4 Save them as Windows Environment Variables
OPEN CMD :
setx TWILIO_SID "YOUR_ACCOUNT_SID"
setx TWILIO_AUTH "YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN"
setx TWILIO_NUMBER "+19804042373"
3.5 Restart your CMD
(so the variables load)

STEP 4 — Run the Backend
Open CMD:
cd backend
venv\Scripts\activate
python app.py
Correct output will show:
Twilio configured: True
Running on http://127.0.0.1:5000
Backend is done ✔

STEP 5 — Setup Frontend
5.1 Go to frontend folder:
cd frontend
5.2 Create package.json (I provided it)
5.3 Install dependencies:
npm install
5.4 Run the frontend:
npm run dev
It will show:
Local: http://localhost:5173/
Open that link.

STEP 6 – Setup Elder-UI and run
Open CMD:
cd elder-ui
python -m http.server 8000
Open in browser - http://localhost:8000/index.html

STEP 7— FIRST TIME USE
When frontend opens:
1️⃣ Signup using email + password
2️⃣ It logs you in
3️⃣ Build your profile (your name + phone)
4️⃣ Add family members
5️⃣ Go to Analyze page
6️⃣ Paste any SCAM message
7️⃣ Click Analyze

STEP 8 — SMS Alert Works Automatically
If AI detects scam:
✔ Alert goes to YOUR phone
✔ Alert goes to ALL family numbers
✔ Alert contains scam details
✔ Twilio sends instantly

